title: One in four Ukip voters believe aliens have made contact - but government is hiding it
text: UKIP One in four Ukip voters believe aliens have made contact - but government is hiding it YouGov survey finds Ukip voters most likely to believe that extra-terrestrial life has made contact but the government is suppressing the news E.T. from Steven Spielberg's 1982 blockbuster E.T. The Extra-Terrestrial Photo: UNIVERSAL By Michael Wilkinson , Political Correspondent 10:11AM BST 13 Oct 2015
